{
  "texts": [
    "Managing the ability to track of the media, the transmission infrastructure, and the transactions is the key to BC's capacity to prevent digital deceit.",
    "However, there are still issues to be solved in terms of creating efficient methods for information identification, testing, transmission, and auditing (Fraga-Lamas and Fernández-Caramés 2020).",
    "Therefore, the goal of this section is to leverage on BC technology as a way to guarantee digital content authentication.",
    "In this regard, we review in Sect. 4.1 several interesting works that can help the reader to better understand the potential of this technology as an open research spot and its future applications.",
    "Moreover, some insights are discussed in Sect. 4.2."
  ]
}